description: This file contains a collection of API implementations for managing WAN interfaces in a network device, including get/set functions for various interface parameters, validation, commit and rollback operations, and handling specific configurations like IP, MAPT, and Physical interface details.

methods.name: BOOL WanIfMapt_SetParamStringValue(ANSC_HANDLE hInsContext,char * ParamName,char * pString)
methods.description: Sets the MAPT parameter string value in the WAN interface context, specifically the 'Path' parameter when FEATURE_MAPT is enabled.

methods.name: BOOL WanIfMapt_Validate(ANSC_HANDLE hInsContext,char * pReturnParamName,ULONG * puLength)
methods.description: Validation function for MAPT settings, currently always returns TRUE indicating success.

methods.name: ULONG WanIfMapt_Commit(ANSC_HANDLE hInsContext)
methods.description: Commits MAPT configuration changes, currently a stub returning 0.

methods.name: ULONG WanIfMapt_Rollback(ANSC_HANDLE hInsContext)
methods.description: Rolls back MAPT configuration changes, currently a stub returning 0.

methods.name: BOOL WanIfDSLite_GetParamUlongValue(ANSC_HANDLE hInsContext,char * ParamName,ULONG * puLong)
methods.description: Retrieves the ULONG value of the 'Status' parameter for DSLite WAN interface.

methods.name: BOOL WanIfDSLite_SetParamUlongValue(ANSC_HANDLE hInsContext,char * ParamName,ULONG uValue)
methods.description: Sets the ULONG value of the 'Status' parameter for DSLite WAN interface.

methods.name: ULONG WanIfDSLite_GetParamStringValue(ANSC_HANDLE hInsContext,char * ParamName,char * pValue,ULONG * pUlSize)
methods.description: Retrieves the string value of the 'Path' parameter for DSLite WAN interface, handling buffer size return codes.

methods.name: BOOL WanIfDSLite_SetParamStringValue(ANSC_HANDLE hInsContext,char * ParamName,char * pString)
methods.description: Sets the string value of the 'Path' parameter for DSLite WAN interface.

methods.name: BOOL WanIfDSLite_Validate(ANSC_HANDLE hInsContext,char * pReturnParamName,ULONG * puLength)
methods.description: Validation stub for DSLite interface, always returns TRUE.

methods.name: ULONG WanIfDSLite_Commit(ANSC_HANDLE hInsContext)
methods.description: Commits DSLite configuration, currently a stub returning 0.

methods.name: ULONG WanIfDSLite_Rollback(ANSC_HANDLE hInsContext)
methods.description: Rolls back DSLite configuration, currently a stub returning 0.

methods.name: ULONG Marking_GetEntryCount(ANSC_HANDLE hInsContext)
methods.description: Returns the count of marking entries for a given WAN interface if FEATURE_802_1P_COS_MARKING is enabled.

methods.name: ANSC_HANDLE Marking_GetEntry(ANSC_HANDLE hInsContext,ULONG nIndex,ULONG * pInsNumber)
methods.description: Retrieves a marking entry by index, returning its handle if exists.

methods.name: ANSC_HANDLE Marking_AddEntry(ANSC_HANDLE hInsContext,ULONG * pInsNumber)
methods.description: Adds a new marking entry to the WAN interface's marking list.

methods.name: ULONG Marking_DelEntry(ANSC_HANDLE hInsContext,ANSC_HANDLE hInstance)
methods.description: Deletes a specified marking entry from the list.

methods.name: BOOL Marking_GetParamUlongValue(ANSC_HANDLE hInsContext,char * ParamName,ULONG * puLong)
methods.description: Retrieves ULONG parameters 'SKBPort' and 'SKBMark' from a marking entry.

methods.name: ULONG Marking_GetParamStringValue(ANSC_HANDLE hInsContext,char * ParamName,char * pValue,ULONG * pUlSize)
methods.description: Retrieves string parameter 'Alias' from a marking entry.

methods.name: BOOL Marking_GetParamIntValue(ANSC_HANDLE hInsContext,char * ParamName,int * pInt)
methods.description: Retrieves integer parameter 'EthernetPriorityMark' from a marking entry.

methods.name: BOOL Marking_SetParamUlongValue(ANSC_HANDLE hInsContext,char * ParamName,ULONG uValue)
methods.description: Sets ULONG parameters 'SKBPort' and 'SKBMark' for a marking entry.

methods.name: BOOL Marking_SetParamStringValue(ANSC_HANDLE hInsContext,char * ParamName,char * pString)
methods.description: Sets string parameter 'Alias' for a marking entry, with validation to prevent overwrites.

methods.name: BOOL Marking_SetParamIntValue(ANSC_HANDLE hInsContext,char * ParamName,int iValue)
methods.description: Sets integer parameter 'EthernetPriorityMark' for a marking entry.

methods.name: BOOL Marking_Validate(ANSC_HANDLE hInsContext,char * pReturnParamName,ULONG * puLength)
methods.description: Validation stub for marking, always returns TRUE.

methods.name: ULONG Marking_Commit(ANSC_HANDLE hInsContext)
methods.description: Commits the marking configuration, adding if new, or updating existing entries.

methods.name: ULONG Marking_Rollback(ANSC_HANDLE hInsContext)
methods.description: Rolls back marking changes, currently a stub returning 0.

methods.name: BOOL WanIfPPPCfg_SetParamUlongValue(ANSC_HANDLE hInsContext,char * ParamName,ULONG uValue)
methods.description: Sets ULONG configuration parameters, with support for 'IPCPStatus', 'IPv6CPStatus', 'LinkStatus', others are not supported.

methods.name: ULONG WanIfPPPCfg_GetParamBoolValue(ANSC_HANDLE hInsContext,char * ParamName,BOOL * pBool)
methods.description: Retrieves boolean flags 'Enable', 'IPCPEnable', 'IPv6CPEnable' — currently always FALSE or TRUE with debug info.

methods.name: BOOL WanIfPPPCfg_SetParamBoolValue(ANSC_HANDLE hInsContext,char * ParamName,BOOL bValue)
methods.description: Sets boolean flags; currently mainly logs unsupported changes.

methods.name: BOOL WanIfPPPCfg_Validate(ANSC_HANDLE hInsContext,char * ParamName,BOOL bValue)
methods.description: Validation stub for PPP configuration, always returns TRUE.

methods.name: ULONG WanIfPPPCfg_Commit(ANSC_HANDLE hInsContext)
methods.description: Commits PPP configuration, calling DmlSetWanIfCfg with current data.

methods.name: ULONG WanIfPPPCfg_Rollback(ANSC_HANDLE hInsContext)
methods.description: Rolls back PPP configuration, currently dummy returning TRUE.

methods.name: ULONG WanIfCfg_GetParamStringValue(ANSC_HANDLE hInsContext,char * ParamName,char * pValue,ULONG * pUlSize)
ULONG WanIfMapt_GetParamStringValue(ANSC_HANDLE hInsContext,char * ParamName,char * pValue,ULONG * pUlSize)
ULONG WanIfPhy_GetParamStringValue(ANSC_HANDLE hInsContext,char * ParamName,char * pValue,ULONG * pUlSize)
